# Ownership split: anyone can open PRs anywhere, but merges into
# platform-owned paths require platform-team review. App manifests
# (apps/*/base, apps/*/env, apps/*/chart) are deliberately NOT listed —
# app teams own their deployment config.
#
# Replace @example-org/platform-team with your real team slug.

/bootstrap/          @example-org/platform-team
/apps/*/argocd/      @example-org/platform-team
/apps/*/kargo/       @example-org/platform-team
/.github/            @example-org/platform-team
/docs/               @example-org/platform-team
